{"tid":135922,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【目測有E cup】新歡大起底 阮經天女友原來係長榮空姐","createTime":"2017-02-26T16:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T17:46:16.000Z","uid":29627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c47831f75c64e755955d74932ac00461b9720ace","tid":135922,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:33:56.000Z","msg":"【目測有E cup】新歡大起底 阮經天女友原來係長榮空姐<br />\n<br />\n34歲阮經天(小天)前年同拍拖8年嘅許瑋甯分手，小天多次想復合，不過許瑋甯都未有應承，但近日小天似乎又有新目標，原來佢已經有一個短髮新歡「臉紅妹」!<br />\n<br />\n日前台灣報道指，上周四(23號)見到小天帶新歡同細佬，同友人喺台北松山區寶清街一間火鍋店開餐，報道話小天身邊坐咗喺一個目測約廿歲嘅辣妹身旁有傾有講、辣妹新歡上圍估計有D cup。<br />\n<br />\n食完二人前後腳出門口，最初扮唔識，小天就同友人道別，跟住去拎近百萬嘅媾女跑車，辣妹女伴即自動上車，見附近唔覺有記者，小天先上司機位，送個女仔返香閨。事後小天經理人就話：「他(小天)目前單身，那個女生不是新女友，只是從英國回來的朋友，大家一起吃個飯。」<br />\n<br />\n有眼利網民事後將小天新歡大起底，指佢其實係長榮空姐，記者搵到空姐嘅Ig，Ig暱稱叫FaFa照片中有當日同小天吃火鍋着嘅同一件粉紫色衫，仲有佢嘅泳裝照，澎湃上圍睇嚟至少E cup。事後FaFa唔知係咪道俾人起底，噚晚已將Ig帳號成個剷走。記者詢問小天經理人「臉紅妹」係咪「FaFa」空姐 ，經理人暫時未有回覆。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170226/56356145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170226%2F56356145&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=58dfbf2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170226%2F56356145&h=9b7b1ddc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170226/56356145</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170226/large/1488091980_2a25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170226%2Flarge%2F1488091980_2a25.jpg&h=111c6af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170226/large/1488091982_f0f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170226%2Flarge%2F1488091982_f0f9.jpg&h=97e0995a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170226/large/1488091983_d8e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170226%2Flarge%2F1488091983_d8e9.jpg&h=3840852f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170226/large/1488091984_db8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170226%2Flarge%2F1488091984_db8d.jpg&h=a63bd5c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170226/large/1488091985_5633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170226%2Flarge%2F1488091985_5633.jpg&h=afd44c91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed75eb1d27127f4d59d5d7321a7ca07d8362a8ae","tid":135922,"uid":51512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcbb8a6ade471d22fe962f9565817ba9e96a84e","tid":135922,"uid":52020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T17:42:38.000Z","msg":"阮經天好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b24ee940f3bf0d7cc295bf26c8488a08549148","tid":135922,"uid":73064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T17:44:06.000Z","msg":"台灣通街都係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23dfcf8ee989cdc2252a5b1563644b60f2b9b9b","tid":135922,"uid":2065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"